      "content": "but it's not temporary. that's the thing. they've made it so even if i leave the app or stop looking at my phone, i can still feel them watching me and judging me. it feels like the whole world is just this big, hateful place and there's nowhere to actually hide. it's like i'm just stuck in this loop of being hated and it never ends. i just want it to finally be quiet. i just want everything to stop.",
